sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant SRV as byteswarm Server
    participant BUS as Event Bus
    participant DB as State Store

    Note over SRV,BUS: connection lost — server reboot or network partition
    loop until reconnected (exponential backoff)
        SRV->>BUS: reconnect attempt [NATS]
    end
    BUS-->>SRV: reconnected — resume durable consumer at last cursor [NATS]
    BUS->>SRV: redeliver unacknowledged events [NATS]
    opt stateful consumer
        SRV->>DB: reload state (durable source of truth) [SQL]
        DB-->>SRV: state
    end
    SRV->>SRV: reprocess idempotently
    SRV->>BUS: ack [NATS]
